description: Promithian Global Ventures, Inc., a development stage company, engages in the exploration of mineral properties in Canada. The company explores for silver and copper deposits. It holds interests in the Warburton property located in the Southern Yukon. The company was formerly known as Midex Gold Corp. and changed its name to Promithian Global Ventures, Inc. in May 2013. Promithian Global Ventures, Inc. is based in Salt Lake City, Utah.
